Let (u1,l1) & (u2,l2) be the upper and lower bounds of the two quantities.

In case of addition of bounds:
new width = (u1 + u2 - l2 - l1)/2
	= (w1 + w2)


In case of subtraction of bounds:
case 1:
	new width = [(u1 - l1) - (l1 - u2)]/2
		= w1 + w2
case 2:
	new width = [(u1 - l2) - (l2 - u1)]/2
		= w1 + (l1/2) + w2 - (u2/2)
case 3:
	new width = [(u2 - l2) - (l1 - u2)]/2
		= w2 + (l2/2) + w1 - (l1/2)
case 4:
	new width = [(u2 - l1) - (l2 - u1)]/2
		= w2 + w1
